OL,3,GOPINIONCPam Masters: a key figure in
OL,4,Cmodern British television presentation
OL,5,
OL,6,FPam Masters, whose death has been
OL,7,Fannounced, was probably the single most
OL,8,Fimportant person in the story of modern
OL,9,FBritish television presentation.
OL,11,FAs Channel 4's first head of
OL,12,Fpresentation she helped give the
OL,13,Fupstart channel with a seemingly random
OL,14,Fselection of programmes its on-air
OL,15,Fidentity.
OL,17,FShe commissioned the iconic Channel 4
OL,18,Fidents designed by Martin Lambie-Nairn
OL,19,Fand took responsibility for the
OL,20,Fchannel's promotion strategy.
OL,23,EPub: 10-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
