OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCPam Masters: a key figure in
OL,4,Cmodern British television presentation
OL,5,
OL,6,FHer professionalism helped establish
OL,7,Fthe channel and build its reputation.
OL,9,FBy all accounts, some of the problems
OL,10,Fin the early days required a seasoned
OL,11,Fprofessional who could be calm under
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,FSome independent producers, allegedly,
OL,15,Fdidn't quite get the idea of sticking
OL,16,Fto slot durations. Others didn't seem
OL,17,Fto understand the need to provide music
OL,18,Freporting details.
OL,20,FMasters helped get all this sorted.
OL,23,EPub: 10-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
