OL,3,GOPINIONCPam Masters: a key figure in
OL,4,Cmodern British television presentation
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn 1988 she returned to the BBC and
OL,7,Fbrought with her concepts she'd
OL,8,Fdeveloped at C4.
OL,10,FBBC networks were properly branded for
OL,11,Fthe first time. More data was used to
OL,12,Fdecide how to place promotions to
OL,13,Fmaximise their impact.
OL,15,FLater, Presentation became a business
OL,16,Funit able to win outside clients `
OL,17,Fproof an excellent service could win
OL,18,Fbusiness and cash for the BBC to
OL,19,Freinvest.
OL,23,EPub: 10-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
