OL,3,GOPINIONCPam Masters: a key figure in
OL,4,Cmodern British television presentation
OL,5,
OL,6,FPerhaps inevitably it was sold off and
OL,7,Fbecame Red Bee Media. While Red Bee was
OL,8,Fa huge success, there will be those who
OL,9,Fthought the BBC was selling off the
OL,10,Ffamily silver.
OL,12,FPam Masters spent almost her entire
OL,13,Fworking life in Presentation. She
OL,14,Fworked her way through the ranks and as
OL,15,Fa manager knew what jobs actually
OL,16,Finvolved.
OL,18,FShe was also one of the most senior
OL,19,Fwomen in television.
OL,23,EPub: 10-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
